<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink392">
<l>vēyvaṉap piḻanta tōḷum veyiṟeṟa</l>
<l>vāykaviṉ ṟolainta nutalu nōkkip</l>
<l>pariyal vāḻi tōḻi pariyi</l>
<l>ṉellaiyi liṭumpai tarūu</l>
<l>nalvarai nāṭaṉoṭu vanta māṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>May you live long my friend! Don’t feel sad,</l>
<l>looking at my arms that have lost their bamboo elegance,  </l>
<l>and at my forehead that lost beauty due to the scorching sun, </l>
<l>If you feel sad, these changes that came with the lord of good mountains,  </l>
<l>cause me endless affliction!  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
